release_note: New in camera FX menu allows you to add new effects without leaving the scene A walkthrough of the camera features will help you create your first VFX shot easily! Watermark placement has been improved

New control panel for live editing with camera preview Advanced auto floor detection system Updated effects selection menu

Introduced the ability to place VFX on walls floors and ceilings with LiDAR assisted technology. Improved visual guidelines for intuitive placement fine tuning. Added fun and customisable face tracked effects. Added overlay effects that lock to the camera s view. Handy tutorial popups to guide new users through their first VFX shot. Introduced an accessible video album multi delete tool. Improved account deletion process Several bug fixes and optimisations
